Astroplate provides everything you need to jumpstart your Astro project. Get started with Astroplate and save yourself hours of work.


## Features

* Multi-Authors
* Multilingual
* Similar Posts Suggestion
* Search Functionality
* Dark Mode
* Tags & Categories
* Netlify setting pre-configured
* Support contact form
* Fully responsive
* Write and update content in Markdown / MDX
* Disqus Comment
* Syntax Highlighting
